  "detailed_description": "<h1>ADD US TO YOUR WISHLIST!</h1><p><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/814680/extras/SpecWL_(1).png?t=1555499733\" ></p><br><h1>Follow Unbound Progress:</h1><p><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/814680/extras/Discord_icon.png?t=1555499733\" > <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://discord.gg/3gU8Amb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Discord Channel</a><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/814680/extras/Twitter.png?t=1555499733\" > <a href=\"https://twitter.com/UnboundTheGame\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Twitter Unbound</a><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/814680/extras/facebook-icon-png-32x32-6.png?t=1555499733\" > <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.facebook.com/UnboundGame/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Facebook Unbound</a></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Unbound is an atmospheric 2D Puzzle-Platformer where the main character, Soli, can conjure magic portals to travel between different realities in order to learn more about the catastrophe that ravaged his world. Inside certain portals, the physical properties of the  character or world elements can change, offering new gameplay possibilities.<br><br>Unbound\u2019s artistic approach can be summarized as a dark fairy tale presented in a cartoonish style, with the purpose to give the game experience a fresh look and feel. Curiosity and exploration will have an impact on the overall atmosphere .",
  "about_the_game": "Unbound is an atmospheric 2D Puzzle-Platformer where the main character, Soli, can conjure magic portals to travel between different realities in order to learn more about the catastrophe that ravaged his world. Inside certain portals, the physical properties of the  character or world elements can change, offering new gameplay possibilities.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUnbound\u2019s artistic approach can be summarized as a dark fairy tale presented in a cartoonish style, with the purpose to give the game experience a fresh look and feel. Curiosity and exploration will have an impact on the overall atmosphere .",
  "short_description": "Explore beautiful, hand-crafted worlds using portals. Solve puzzles by using the enemies to your advantage, and progress through your adventure at their expense!",
